<div class="hmk chat-card item-card">
    <header class="card-header flexrow">
        <h3 class="title">Face the Pall</h3>
    </header>

    {{#if actorName}}
    <div class="card-content center">
        <span>{{actorName}} must face the Pall — the choice is theirs.</span>
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="card-content">
        <span
            >The Pall cannot be expelled. The victim must choose one of three
            fates:</span
        >
    </div>

    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Embrace the Pall</strong> — the soul is imprisoned; the body
            persists as an undead Nightwight.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Vacate the Body</strong> — the soul unanchors into a Shade;
            the empty body becomes a mindless Helthraal.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Accept True Death</strong> — the soul departs to the
            afterlife; the body allows only a brief moment as a Helthraal.
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
